    "description": "自由搭配华丽的战技、改变游戏玩法的装备，以及可进化的技能。从超过20位可操作角色中打造出无敌队伍，在这场精彩刺激的冒险中，完成50个以上的剧情任务，探索其他丰富内容。《受赞颂者斩2》强势回归，再创巅峰！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074850/extras/493d28c8c36ade36ee3d0e13724af338.poster.avif?t=1772001445\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074850/extras/493d28c8c36ade36ee3d0e13724af338.webm?t=1772001445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074850/extras/493d28c8c36ade36ee3d0e13724af338.mp4?t=1772001445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验《虚伪的假面》之后的故事！[/i]</h2>主线剧情“白皇演武”以《二人的白皇》为基础，围绕“战记”这一主轴展开。同时新增大量全语音新剧情“武人传”，带来全新的故事体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏类型进化为“3D动作RPG”！</h2>新增技能板和刷子要素，大幅强化RPG可玩性，让玩家可以慢慢享受培育角色的乐趣。<br>游戏内设有据点“恩那卡姆依宅邸”。玩家可以在据点内进行推进剧情、强化角色、增进和伙伴之间的交流等操作。据点可通过在游戏内获得的点数来进行扩张。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074850/extras/14dbb0f27784eb11550b854980ab2416.poster.avif?t=1772001445\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074850/extras/14dbb0f27784eb11550b854980ab2416.webm?t=1772001445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074850/extras/14dbb0f27784eb11550b854980ab2416.mp4?t=1772001445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情演出焕然一新！</h2>剧情模式不再只有立绘和文字，而是采用3D建模，注重情境渲染和人物位置关系，以更具动画风格的形式演绎故事。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >内置线上模式“梦幻演武”！</h2>内置线上合作模式“梦幻演武”。在此模式下，玩家可通过联机合作，共同完成任务。设有该模式独有的敌人和地图。离线模式下亦可游玩。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074850/extras/d948633fe6a3266db809c6fcef986c8d.poster.avif?t=1772001445\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074850/extras/d948633fe6a3266db809c6fcef986c8d.webm?t=1772001445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074850/extras/d948633fe6a3266db809c6fcef986c8d.mp4?t=1772001445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
